See Disney’s Encanto only in theaters November 24.

Sea the new treats making a splash at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon and Disney’s Blizzard Beach! 🤩🌊

☀️ DOLE Whip Watermelon with Chamoy and Chili-Lime Spice at Snack Shack at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon: DOLE Whip Watermelon topped off with chamoy and zesty chili-lime spice

☀️ Soft-serve Cookie Sandwich at Happy Landings Ice Cream and Snack Shack at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon: Vanilla soft-serve sandwiched between two chocolate chip cookies and rolled in chocolate sprinkles or rainbow sprinkles

☀️ S’mores Churro at I.C. Expeditions at Disney’s Blizzard Beach: Churro pieces topped with graham cracker crumbs, marshmallow whipped cream, chocolate sauce, and toasted mini marshmallows

Look at what treasure washed ashore! Discover the Mermaid Lagoon Mug at Trader Sam’s Enchanted Tiki Bar at the @disneyland Hotel 🧜‍♀️🍹

✨ Snag the Disneyland 70th Celebration Mermaid Lagoon Mug: Disney Artist Showcase featuring Coppertop via mobile order only on the Disneyland app on July 24, while supplies last!

✨ Mobile Orders can be placed through the Trader Sam’s Mug Release listing as early as 6 a.m. PT on July 24

✨ Arrival windows for designated pickup hours are between 8 a.m. to 5 p.m. PT and pickup is in the Grand Ballroom at the Disneyland Hotel

✨Be among the first to purchase and have your mug signed by the artist where you can also enjoy music, themed photo-ops, and more when you pick up your mug!

✨Find the mug at Trader Sam’s Enchanted Tiki Bar on July 25, while supplies last!

#DisneyEats #Disneyland #TraderSams #Disneyland70

Red, white, and sweet treats! Don’t miss the patriotic eats coming to @waltdisneyworld from June 29 to July 5! 🎆🍽️

⭐️ NEW! Patriotic Cake Bar at Amorette’s Patisserie: Vanilla chiffon combined with passion fruit, orange, and guava juice

⭐️ NEW! Caramel-Apple Pie Funnel Cake at Epic Eats: Funnel cake with apple pie topping, caramel drizzle, and vanilla soft-serve (Currently available beyond July 5)

⭐️ NEW! Red, White, and Blue Waffle at Sleepy Hollow: Waffle topped with mixed berries, vanilla ice cream, whipped cream, and festive sprinkles

⭐️ Berry Shortcake at Columbia Harbour House: Shortcake topped with mixed berries, whipped cream, and patriotic sprinkles

⭐️ Red, White, and Blue Funnel Cake at Sleepy Hollow: Funnel cake topped with mixed berries, vanilla ice cream, whipped cream, and festive sprinkles

⭐️ Red, White, and Blue Slushy at Liberty Square Market: Frozen Fanta Blue Raspberry and Fanta Cherry layered with whipped cream and topped with popping candies
